"""
File: Week 1 Day 2 - operations with 2 variables
Purpose: Practice using two variables to calculate:
         - addition (+)
         - subtraction (-)
         - multiplication (*)
         - decimal division (/)
         - integer division (//)
         Document the difference between / and //
         Calculate rectangle area
Date: 2026-05-03
